-----  ATCsim DESCRIPTION  -----

ATCsim (Air Traffic Control simulation) is the 2013 project of an introduction course on object-oriented programming in C++ at EPFL (CS-118).
It simulates an (obviously simplified) Air Traffic Control workstation like the ones operators play in reality (for example at Skyguide).

